\sum\limits_{k=1}^{\infty}\dfrac{(k!)^2}{(2k)!}
\lim\limits_{k\to\infty}\dfrac{((k+1)!)^2}{(2k+2)!}\cdot\dfrac{(2k)!}{(k!)^2}
\lim\limits_{k\to\infty}\dfrac{((k+1)(k!))^2}{(2k+2)(2k+1){(2k)}!}\cdot\dfrac{(2k)!}{(k!)^2}
\lim\limits_{k\to\infty}\dfrac{(k+1)^2}{(2k+2)(2k+1)}
k^2
\dfrac{1}{4} < 1
1 \leq j \leq k,
(j + k) \geq 2 j.
 \frac{(k!)^2}{(2k)!} = \prod_{j=1}^k \frac{j}{j+k} \leq  \prod_{j=1}^k \frac{1}{2} = \frac{1}{2^k} 
  \frac{j+k}{j} = 1 + \frac{k}{j} \geq 1 + 1 = 2,  
 \frac{j}{j+k} \leq \frac{1}{2}  
